### List all schools
GET {{baseUrl}}/super-admin/schools?page=1&limit=10&sort_field=created_at&sort_dir=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{super-adminToken}}

### List schools with filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/super-admin/schools?search=DPS&city=Delhi&status=active&subscription_status=ACTIVE
Authorization: Bearer {{super-adminToken}}

### Get school by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/super-admin/schools/{{schoolId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{super-adminToken}}

### Toggle school status (activate/deactivate)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/super-admin/schools/{{schoolId}}/toggle-status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{super-adminToken}}

{
  "is_active": false
}

### Get schools stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/super-admin/schools/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{super-adminToken}}

### Get unique cities
GET {{baseUrl}}/super-admin/schools/cities
Authorization: Bearer {{super-adminToken}}